{
  "stem": "22734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I don't know why we fought so much, so terribly not-- to get out of the September transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that's why we survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because the September transport was-- they-- they established this family camp in Birkenau, B, Roman two, B.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then, we came at Christmastime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Nobody was gassed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nobody was shaved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They-- they took our clothes away, our stuff away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But they left-- left us, I think, our shoes-- not-- not-- not shoes, no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They left us something, jackets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They didn't issue us any clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And-- and on March-- in March '44, the-- the people from the September transport, they were told they were going to be moved to a different camp because this camp is overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they were going to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they gave them even a name they gave to this camp-- [NON-ENGLISH], I don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Anyhow, they-- they-- but the guys from the registry were Polish Jews and who had free access to all the camps, could walk back and forth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They came and said, this doesn't look good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "This really doesn't look good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there is a big-- they called the gassing [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "The big action is being prepared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they moved them from this BWB.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "If we want to look at the map next door, which was called quarantine camp just over the wire.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You know, we all saw them there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And then at night, at 7 o'clock, there was a-- something that's called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They called a-- they-- you weren't allowed out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They came with trucks and dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they went, all 5,000 of them, that night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around the corner to the gas chamber--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--all of them with dogs and SS and screaming and screeching.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all heard it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all witnessed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
